Years pass as he hones his body into an unstoppable instrument capable of inflicting unsurpassed damage to opponents in the form of The Thunderbolt Fist!
 Predating the similar Jet Li film Fearless, this epic frenzy of bone-snapping mayhem is an action-packed crowd pleaser that will blow you away! 
Includes the original rare English-dubbed version!
